    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exist.EXE 是一款像素风的解谜冒险游戏，你将扮演 Marcus，一个正因母亲的离世而深陷悲痛的游戏开发者。某天，他被卷入一个数码世界并且发现他的程序编写能力可以用来“骇入”并改变对象数据。 <br>在这里，修改物体数据不只是为了解开谜题，更能够将令人悲伤的事件转化为片刻的喜悦，哪怕只有一瞬间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着 Marcus 深入探索这个数码世界，他的冒险也将成为一次自我探索的旅程。 <br>一个与母亲相似的人工智能希望他永远留在这个完美的数字世界里，远离悲伤；但他的挚友却提醒他，应该回到现实，而不是沉溺于虚假的完美之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>独特的剧情冒险</strong><br></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在触动人心的情境中，你将发现自己能够改变世界，让一切变得更好。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>深刻的个人旅程</strong><br></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被困在数字世界的 Marcus 踏上一段面对悲伤的自我探索之旅。最终，他必须在直面现实与停留在虚假的完美世界之间作出抉择。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>创新的骇入解谜玩法</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过直觉且易上手的机制<strong>骇</strong>入改变周遭的数据。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282860/extras/fd8fce7a6970426197c0ab0906cef6a7.poster.avif?t=1757314935\" width=800 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282860/extras/fd8fce7a6970426197c0ab0906cef6a7.webm?t=1757314935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282860/extras/fd8fce7a6970426197c0ab0906cef6a7.mp4?t=1757314935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>沉浸式数码世界</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结合怀旧像素画风与现代设计元素营造独特而引人入胜的视觉风格。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282860/extras/83bdd210f5a276f80541d78ee3dc68ae.poster.avif?t=1757314935\" width=800 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282860/extras/83bdd210f5a276f80541d78ee3dc68ae.webm?t=1757314935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282860/extras/83bdd210f5a276f80541d78ee3dc68ae.mp4?t=1757314935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>设计・创造・挑战</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用内建的关卡编辑器打造专属谜题，并与社区分享你的创作，向其他玩家发起挑战。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282860/extras/2b3d6bfa56dee8c81745eba0f06b3f5c.poster.avif?t=1757314935\" width=1092 height=614 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282860/extras/2b3d6bfa56dee8c81745eba0f06b3f5c.webm?t=1757314935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282860/extras/2b3d6bfa56dee8c81745eba0f06b3f5c.mp4?t=1757314935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
